[[div_ class="stanza one"]]
[[div_ class="chinese"]]
痛兮生哉
观亦由之
匿亦由之
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="english"]]
Painful is birth
with that we see
in that we hide.
[[/div]]
[[/div]]

